{"tid":377742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又有仆街學校]元朗惇裕學校現影子學生","createTime":"2017-08-28T02:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T02:34:51.000Z","uid":59849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"200f62f02134efb191b783a868b611ccb4ffeafe","tid":377742,"uid":59849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"繼屯門興德學校被揭有「影子學生」後，本報發現位於元朗新田的惇裕學校同樣出現「影子學生」。<br />\n<br />\n本報獲得該校共5張成績表，至少涉及3個學生，在長時間缺席及沒有考試的情況下仍獲升班。校方回覆時承認事件，解釋該數名學生突然失去聯絡，基於人情保留其學位，並已通報教育局。<br />\n<br />\n教育局則指校方的呈報及跟進程序須改善，亦不應為沒有合理原因而長期缺席的學生保留學位。<br />\n<br />\n至於校方其後如何處理長期缺課情況？詳情請留意今天《明報》報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170828/s00001/1503848134540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170828%2Fs00001%2F1503848134540&d=4B2rI1UwQJXGe7zbu6YXSI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8d6a162a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170828%2Fs00001%2F1503848134540&h=97a81920\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170828/s00001/1503848134540</a>"},{"pid":"b7ec2b72b1b5d0d97ad3d7cb3bf6ed827df0fe54","tid":377742,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:21:40.000Z","msg":"全部北區學校有可疑"},{"pid":"d66bb780408f70faac58c3006fb3ff3f5fa58407","tid":377742,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"元屯天"},{"pid":"c1f860971eec93bc726c0db10836bf7de53bcd65","tid":377742,"uid":76330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:34:51.000Z","msg":"有幾出奇？成個制度+跨境學生+on9土皇帝教畜根本就鼓吹緊呢啲事<br />\n<br />\n呢間野9成5係單雙非，on99咁<br />\n都係為左食哂D蝗蟲仔先畀佢存在既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}